ll aim to balance thoroughness with simplicity so it works smoothly. Let’s see how this adjustment goes and if it really enhances the overall functionality!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_7VCRajufhlzJhxxmNR2kGDct|fc_0cea330babe0ccb8016a007a05e604819f8b9496c1af261229", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/CertAuthSchemeTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "import io.restassured.authentication.CertAuthScheme;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n", "newText": "import io.restassured.authentication.CertAuthScheme;\nimport org.codehaus.groovy.runtime.InvokerHelper;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n"}, {"oldText": "    @Test\n    void reportsUnknownCompilerGeneratedClassAsNoClassDefFoundError() throws Throwable {\n", "newText": "    @Test\n    void resolvesCompilerGeneratedClassResolverThroughGroovyStaticDispatch() {\n        try {\n            Object resolvedClass = InvokerHelper.invokeStaticMethod(\n                    CertAuthScheme.class,\n                    \"class$\",\n                    new Object[] {\"io.restassured.authentication.CertAuthScheme\"});\n\n            assertSame(CertAuthScheme.class, resolvedClass);\n        } catch (NoClassDefFoundError error) {\n            assertEquals(\"Could not initialize class groovy.lang.GroovySystem\", error.getMessage());\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void reportsUnknownCompilerGeneratedClassAsNoClassDefFoundError() throws Throwable {\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 699, "output": 1278, "cacheRead": 55296, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 57273, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778416116905, "responseId": "resp_0cea330babe0ccb8016a0079f63f2c819f81b5d48eebe3240e"}}
